WEBVTT

1
00:00:07.957 --> 00:00:12.791
<i>GODFREY [ON TV]: So the Justice League
finally provided scanners...</i>

2
00:00:12.886 --> 00:00:14.923
<i>to every government on Earth...</i>

3
00:00:15.089 --> 00:00:18.263
<i>to root out those
filthy little aliens...</i>

4
00:00:18.425 --> 00:00:21.372
<i>posing as real human beings.</i>

5
00:00:21.528 --> 00:00:27.843
<i>But you have to wonder. how were they
able to whip up this tech so fast?</i>

6
00:00:28.001 --> 00:00:32.780
<i>Or more accurately.
how long have they been keeping it from us?</i>

7
00:00:32.940 --> 00:00:37.150
<i>Oh. sure. they offer it up
like a gift from the gods.</i>

8
00:00:37.311 --> 00:00:39.951
Sit anywhere. kids.

9
00:00:40.581 --> 00:00:41.889
[GASPS]

10
00:01:11.011 --> 00:01:12.354
[GRUNTS]

11
00:01:15.682 --> 00:01:20.131
There's only one Bibbo.
and don't you forget it.

12
00:01:25.259 --> 00:01:27.261
[GROWLING]

13
00:01:41.141 --> 00:01:45.487
Huh. Boy.
That practically singed my eyebrows off.

14
00:01:45.646 --> 00:01:48.422
Yeah. Practically.

15
00:01:48.582 --> 00:01:51.961
- Uh. you got a little sc...
- Blue. scan for it!

16
00:01:52.119 --> 00:01:54.929
Right. right. Scanning.

17
00:01:56.290 --> 00:01:59.794
Sorry. Nothing. He's gone.

18
00:01:59.960 --> 00:02:04.966
No. it would not have been preferable
to vaporize him back at the diner.

19
00:02:19.546 --> 00:02:20.752
BLACK MANTA:
Welcome aboard.

20
00:02:23.617 --> 00:02:25.062
Dive.

21
00:02:35.395 --> 00:02:40.053
<b> Season 2: Invasion
Episode 3: "Alienated"</b>

22
00:02:40.281 --> 00:02:43.281
Subripped by Reef
www.addic7ed.com

23
00:02:49.276 --> 00:02:51.688
MAN:
Sir? We've received the Rannian signal.

24
00:02:53.780 --> 00:02:55.589
They're arriving now.

25
00:02:56.250 --> 00:02:59.891
<i>COMPUTER:
Recognized: Adam Strange. A-1-1.</i>

26
00:03:00.053 --> 00:03:03.091
<i>Miss Martian. 5-0-5.</i>

27
00:03:03.257 --> 00:03:08.536
Superboy. 5-0-4.
Beast Boy. 5-1-9.

28
00:03:08.695 --> 00:03:09.895
BEAST BOY:
Nightwing!

29
00:03:09.930 --> 00:03:12.433
Check out my super-cool alien souvenir.

30
00:03:12.599 --> 00:03:15.307
<i>MISS MARTIAN: Gar. Business first.
BEAST BOY: Noted.</i>

31
00:03:15.469 --> 00:03:17.073
Zeta Squad. report.

32
00:03:17.237 --> 00:03:21.242
Our mission to neutralize the Krolotean's
Zeta-Platforms on Rann was a success.

33
00:03:21.408 --> 00:03:23.684
I've brought back specs
to create a Zeta-Shield...

34
00:03:23.844 --> 00:03:26.916
to prevent any more aliens
from beaming to Earth from off-world.

35
00:03:27.080 --> 00:03:29.754
How will that affect
our own Zeta-capabilities?

36
00:03:29.917 --> 00:03:33.729
It won't. The Shield will activate at an
altitude above the Watchtower's orbit.

37
00:03:33.887 --> 00:03:36.060
League Zeta-Tubes
will still function normally.

38
00:03:36.223 --> 00:03:39.397
Tell them about Rimbor.
Tell them about the 15 hours.

39
00:03:42.496 --> 00:03:45.500
MISS MARTIAN:
It may be easier to show you.

40
00:03:48.535 --> 00:03:52.005
<i>I successfully interrogated
a Krolotean general on Rann...</i>

41
00:03:52.172 --> 00:03:55.153
<i>who had paid off a member
of the Rannian Science Command...</i>

42
00:03:55.309 --> 00:03:59.815
<i>to allow the Kroloteans to land
a secret base in the Rannian jungle.</i>

43
00:03:59.980 --> 00:04:03.655
<i>Once there. the Kroloteans stole
Zeta-Platform technology...</i>

44
00:04:03.817 --> 00:04:06.627
<i>from Adam Strange's friend. Sardath.</i>

45
00:04:06.787 --> 00:04:08.858
<i>They landed another ship
in New Orleans...</i>

46
00:04:09.022 --> 00:04:13.198
<i>and used the Zeta-Platforms to beam
a few hundred Kroloteans to Earth.</i>

47
00:04:13.360 --> 00:04:15.931
<i>They built more platforms.
brought in more Kroloteans...</i>

48
00:04:16.096 --> 00:04:19.168
<i>and began
abducting and replacing humans.</i>

49
00:04:19.333 --> 00:04:23.611
Perhaps as part of an invasion strategy.
though that's still unclear.

50
00:04:23.770 --> 00:04:24.970
But why Earth?

51
00:04:25.072 --> 00:04:28.110
And what does any of this have to do
with the 15 hours?

52
00:04:28.275 --> 00:04:30.721
MISS MARTIAN:
<i>Well. as you know...</i>

53
00:04:30.877 --> 00:04:36.122
<i>five years ago. Vandal Savage placed
the entire League under his control.</i>

54
00:04:36.283 --> 00:04:39.457
<i>Six leaguers:
Superman. Batman. Wonder Woman...</i>

55
00:04:39.620 --> 00:04:42.499
<i>Martian Manhunter. Green Lantern
and Hawkwoman...</i>

56
00:04:42.656 --> 00:04:45.728
<i>went missing
for a full 16 hours.</i>

57
00:04:46.660 --> 00:04:50.130
<i>It turns out you were teleported
to a planet called Rimbor...</i>

58
00:04:50.297 --> 00:04:53.073
<i>where you spent 16 hours on a rampage...</i>

59
00:04:53.467 --> 00:04:55.856
<i>attacking everyone
and everything in sight...</i>

60
00:04:55.895 --> 00:04:58.419
<i>and announcing in several
alien languages</i>

61
00:04:58.445 --> 00:05:00.674
<i>that you were the Justice League
from Earth...</i>

62
00:05:00.707 --> 00:05:03.051
<i>and that the rest of the galaxy
should beware.</i>

63
00:05:04.044 --> 00:05:05.819
That's why the Kroloteans came.

64
00:05:05.979 --> 00:05:08.516
The League itself
brought Earth to their attention.

65
00:05:09.516 --> 00:05:14.226
I don't know what to say.
I have no memories of this. None.

66
00:05:14.388 --> 00:05:18.234
Don't blame yourself.
Blame Savage and his Light.

67
00:05:18.392 --> 00:05:23.637
But John. how is it that you haven't heard
about this intergalactic incident'?

68
00:05:23.797 --> 00:05:26.876
No clue. Rimbor's not a planet
in my sector.

69
00:05:26.911 --> 00:05:28.678
But I'll head to Oa
immediately.

70
00:05:28.686 --> 00:05:31.914
to consult with the Guardians of
the Universe and Green Lantern Corps.

71
00:05:32.072 --> 00:05:35.053
We'll get to the bottom of this. Cap.
I promise.

72
00:05:35.208 --> 00:05:36.408
In the meantime...

73
00:05:36.510 --> 00:05:39.821
we still have a Krolotean invasion force
to track down on Earth.

74
00:05:39.980 --> 00:05:42.961
You did good work on Rann.
Now we need you...

75
00:05:43.517 --> 00:05:45.861
<i>at the Hall of Justice.</i>

76
00:05:49.322 --> 00:05:51.324
[CHILDREN CHATTERING]

77
00:06:01.468 --> 00:06:05.917
CATHERINE: And finally. we have
the four surviving host bodies...

78
00:06:06.073 --> 00:06:11.182
mused by a race of alien energy beings
known as the Appelaxians...

79
00:06:11.344 --> 00:06:14.348
who attempted to conquer the Earth.

80
00:06:14.881 --> 00:06:19.830
Of course. the attack also brought together
Earth's mightiest heroes...

81
00:06:19.986 --> 00:06:22.557
to form the Justice League.

82
00:06:22.723 --> 00:06:26.227
G. Gordon Godfrey says the League
is working with the aliens.

83
00:06:26.393 --> 00:06:30.000
Ahem. This way to the viewing gallery.

84
00:06:31.965 --> 00:06:35.503
<i>MISS MARTIAN: You didn't have to come along.
SUPERBOY: I think I did.</i>

85
00:06:35.669 --> 00:06:38.775
This is the Krolotean
captured by Lagoon Boy. Robin and Beetle?

86
00:06:38.939 --> 00:06:41.442
Your uncle has been interrogating him
for days...

87
00:06:41.608 --> 00:06:45.021
but simply achieving psychic translation
has proven difficult.

88
00:06:45.178 --> 00:06:48.716
In the meantime. the League and the Team
have hunted the Kroloteans...

89
00:06:48.882 --> 00:06:50.919
that had been masquerading
as humans.

90
00:06:51.084 --> 00:06:56.500
But all have escaped capture. despite the fact
that we destroyed their Zeta-Platforms here...

91
00:06:56.656 --> 00:07:00.627
and on Rann. and that they.
apparently. destroyed their own ship.

92
00:07:00.794 --> 00:07:02.796
[GROWLING]

93
00:07:04.531 --> 00:07:08.206
<i>After your success on Rann. Captain Atom
thought you might be of some assis...</i>

94
00:07:08.368 --> 00:07:10.780
The Kroloteans have an emergency
rendezvous point...

95
00:07:10.937 --> 00:07:15.215
and have standing orders
in case of discovery to evacuate there.

96
00:07:15.375 --> 00:07:17.218
A base inside a volcano...

97
00:07:17.711 --> 00:07:20.157
<i>on Malina Island.</i>

98
00:07:48.942 --> 00:07:50.944
[IN ALIEN LANGUAGE]

99
00:07:55.782 --> 00:07:58.262
BLACK MANTA 1: We have arrived
with the final shipment of Kroloteans.

100
00:07:58.418 --> 00:08:01.160
<i>BLACK MANTA 2 [ON SCREEN]:
Congratulations. my son.</i>

101
00:08:01.955 --> 00:08:05.664
Thank you. Father.
Initiating Phase Two.

102
00:08:12.477 --> 00:08:16.220
<i>BATMAN: Remember. this is
primarily a recon mission.</i>

103
00:08:16.381 --> 00:08:20.479
We wanna discover all we can
about the Kroloteans' invasion strategy...

104
00:08:20.509 --> 00:08:24.719
before we shut them down and deliver
them to the Green Lantern Corps.

105
00:08:24.956 --> 00:08:27.596
NIGHTWING:
Approaching drop-zone Beta.

106
00:08:42.641 --> 00:08:43.881
[IN ATLANTEAN]

107
00:08:44.309 --> 00:08:45.549
[IN ATLANTEAN]

108
00:08:54.186 --> 00:08:56.097
Drop-zone Gamma.

109
00:09:00.725 --> 00:09:02.432
[CRASHING]

110
00:09:21.646 --> 00:09:23.592
[IN ALIEN LANGUAGE]

111
00:09:23.782 --> 00:09:25.557
[IN ALIEN LANGUAGE]

112
00:09:26.051 --> 00:09:27.587
[IN ALIEN LANGUAGE]

113
00:09:30.121 --> 00:09:32.123
[KROLOTEANS GROWLING]

114
00:09:45.804 --> 00:09:48.910
- All sectors. report status.
MAN 1 [OVER RADIO]: <i>Sector One. secure.</i>

115
00:09:49.074 --> 00:09:50.815
MAN 2:
Sector Two. secure.

116
00:09:50.976 --> 00:09:52.250
MAN 3:
Sector Four. secure.

117
00:09:52.811 --> 00:09:55.382
Sector Three. report status.

118
00:09:56.948 --> 00:09:58.894
[OVER RADIO]
Sector Three. report.

119
00:10:22.574 --> 00:10:27.182
AQUALAD [IN BLACK MANTA'S VOICE]:
Intruders. Upper Level. And in the water.

120
00:10:30.048 --> 00:10:31.789
GUARD:
There.

121
00:10:33.184 --> 00:10:34.458
[GRUNTING]

122
00:10:43.094 --> 00:10:44.294
[GRUNTS]

123
00:11:00.378 --> 00:11:02.016
[YELLS]

124
00:11:24.703 --> 00:11:27.343
Batgirl. Maneuver Seven.

125
00:11:37.716 --> 00:11:39.718
[BEEPING]

126
00:11:41.419 --> 00:11:43.421
[GUARDS YELLING]

127
00:11:56.334 --> 00:12:00.170
AQUALAD: Manta to Partner. The base
has been infiltrated. Abort operation.

128
00:12:00.222 --> 00:12:03.226
<i>MAN [OVER RADIO]: Partner to Manta.
The device is already primed.</i>

129
00:12:03.274 --> 00:12:06.244
<i>You have five minutes.
Get your men out.</i>

130
00:12:06.277 --> 00:12:11.420
- <i>The bomb will take care of the rest.</i>
- Perfect.

131
00:12:16.462 --> 00:12:20.640
AQUALAD: Manta to all troopers. Endgame
enabled. Strategic retreat to Manta Flyer.

132
00:12:20.670 --> 00:12:23.082
You have four minutes.

133
00:12:27.239 --> 00:12:28.719
NIGHTWING:
Nightwing to Delta Squad.

134
00:12:28.751 --> 00:12:31.027
Enemy is attempting escape.
Request backup.

135
00:12:31.110 --> 00:12:33.112
[YELLING]

136
00:12:42.955 --> 00:12:46.334
- [IN ENGLISH] Nice aim.
- X-ray vision. I cheat.

137
00:12:46.492 --> 00:12:48.529
Superman. triple combo over here.

138
00:12:57.669 --> 00:13:00.548
Quadruple. Nice.

139
00:13:04.910 --> 00:13:06.116
[SCREECHES]

140
00:13:16.822 --> 00:13:19.564
That was amazing.
You just. you just...

141
00:13:19.725 --> 00:13:22.433
whoosh and then
and then. and then. barn!

142
00:13:23.495 --> 00:13:26.135
Little less fan girl.
little more Wonder Girl.

143
00:13:26.465 --> 00:13:28.604
Right. Sorry.

144
00:13:48.220 --> 00:13:50.131
AQUALAD:
Three minutes to departure.

145
00:13:50.289 --> 00:13:52.291
[LAGOON BOY YELLS]

146
00:14:03.836 --> 00:14:06.874
I had not believed Nightwing
until this moment.

147
00:14:07.806 --> 00:14:11.117
- You did not want to believe!
- None of us wanted to believe this!

148
00:14:11.276 --> 00:14:14.655
- How could you betray us?
- You dare question me?

149
00:14:14.813 --> 00:14:17.123
After all of you let Tula die!

150
00:14:18.016 --> 00:14:21.190
Kaldur. that was a mission.
Aquagirl knew the risks!

151
00:14:21.353 --> 00:14:23.390
- No one wanted her to...
LAGOON BOY [IN ENGLISH]: Neptune's beard!

152
00:14:23.555 --> 00:14:25.034
Don't cuddle this traitor.

153
00:14:25.190 --> 00:14:28.000
He has joined forces
with our King's greatest enemy.

154
00:14:28.160 --> 00:14:31.573
Do you mean the King who hid from me
the true identity of my father?

155
00:14:31.730 --> 00:14:34.176
That was my error in judgment.
Kaldur'ahm.

156
00:14:34.333 --> 00:14:36.176
No one else need suffer for it.

157
00:14:36.335 --> 00:14:38.941
All will suffer if Black Manta demands it.

158
00:14:39.104 --> 00:14:41.812
Blood is thicker than seawater.

159
00:14:52.417 --> 00:14:54.055
NIGHTWING:
Kaldur?

160
00:14:55.354 --> 00:14:59.063
Just you and me. old friend?
SUPERBOY: No!

161
00:14:59.224 --> 00:15:02.330
It's a regular reunion special.

162
00:15:02.861 --> 00:15:05.341
Fine. You can take me down...

163
00:15:05.497 --> 00:15:08.273
or you can save everyone
from this bomb.

164
00:15:09.501 --> 00:15:12.243
I am told the yield is quite impressive.

165
00:15:12.404 --> 00:15:13.604
[YELLS]

166
00:15:14.273 --> 00:15:15.946
[GROANING]

167
00:15:16.108 --> 00:15:17.883
You have two minutes.

168
00:15:28.287 --> 00:15:31.291
- They're getting away!
- We'll stop them!

169
00:15:31.456 --> 00:15:33.493
NIGHTWING:
Negative. We have a bomb down here.

170
00:15:33.659 --> 00:15:36.435
- Alien tech. I cannot disarm it.
<i>- I'll get it out.</i>

171
00:15:36.595 --> 00:15:39.701
No!
Might have pressure or motion sensors.

172
00:15:39.865 --> 00:15:42.869
All Squads. evacuate to Bio-Ship. Now.

173
00:15:52.077 --> 00:15:54.887
You heard Nightwing. Move.

174
00:16:01.987 --> 00:16:03.933
Listen! Listen to me!

175
00:16:04.556 --> 00:16:06.558
[IN ALIEN LANGUAGE]

176
00:16:13.165 --> 00:16:17.136
- Neptune's beard.
- [IN MISS MARTIAN'S VOICE] Hello. Megan.

177
00:16:17.302 --> 00:16:19.304
Knew we forgot something.

178
00:16:19.471 --> 00:16:23.009
- Well done. Alpha Squad.
- Find a seat. It's time to go.

179
00:16:23.175 --> 00:16:25.280
Wait. Where's Superman?

180
00:16:25.444 --> 00:16:27.908
Listen! I am not trying to hurt you!

181
00:16:27.963 --> 00:16:30.551
A bomb is set to explode
beneath this base.

182
00:16:30.613 --> 00:16:33.116
There are too many of you
to carry individually...

183
00:16:33.282 --> 00:16:37.389
but if you board your ship.
I will fly you all to safety.

184
00:16:39.455 --> 00:16:41.093
Please!

185
00:16:48.130 --> 00:16:50.132
[BEEPING]

186
00:17:01.310 --> 00:17:03.290
[ALL GRUNTING]

187
00:17:04.480 --> 00:17:06.084
<i>MISS MARTIAN:
Come on. old girl.</i>

188
00:17:37.813 --> 00:17:40.794
He's breathing. Pulse is strong.
He'll be all right.

189
00:17:40.950 --> 00:17:45.126
He didn't save the Kroloteans.
He won't be all right with that.

190
00:17:45.287 --> 00:17:46.487
What just happened?

191
00:17:46.588 --> 00:17:49.125
The Kroloteans were clearly trying
to build a new ship.

192
00:17:49.291 --> 00:17:50.770
They had to. Angelfish.

193
00:17:50.926 --> 00:17:54.806
It was their only way to leave Earth without
their Zeta-Platforms or original ship.

194
00:17:54.964 --> 00:17:58.935
WONDER GIRL: But was Aqualad helping them
escape or luring them into a trap?

195
00:17:59.635 --> 00:18:03.913
The bomb was of alien origin. yet the
Kroloteans clearly knew nothing about it.

196
00:18:04.073 --> 00:18:05.609
So where did it come from?

197
00:18:05.774 --> 00:18:10.689
I have the feeling it may be up to you
and your Team to find out.

198
00:18:21.123 --> 00:18:24.400
- Father.
- Congratulations. son. You did well.

199
00:18:25.060 --> 00:18:28.405
I don't suppose Aquaman
died in the explosion.

200
00:18:28.897 --> 00:18:30.535
Unlikely.

201
00:18:30.899 --> 00:18:32.099
[BLACK MANTA SIGHS]

202
00:18:32.101 --> 00:18:33.301
Pity.

203
00:18:33.302 --> 00:18:35.145
[ALARM WAILING]

204
00:18:35.304 --> 00:18:37.648
If you'll excuse me...

205
00:18:45.280 --> 00:18:47.487
<i>Good morning. Black Manta.</i>

206
00:18:47.649 --> 00:18:53.463
<i>The Krolotean's competitor. our new Partner.
is quite pleased with your efforts.</i>

207
00:18:53.622 --> 00:18:55.465
<i>And so is the Light.</i>

208
00:18:55.624 --> 00:18:57.626
All agree we made the right choice...

209
00:18:57.793 --> 00:19:02.572
<i>asking you to replace
poor. disgraced Ocean Master.</i>

210
00:19:02.731 --> 00:19:07.737
<i>You are officially one with the Light.</i>

211
00:19:19.915 --> 00:19:23.362
- I wish I could go with.
- I doubt your mother would approve.

212
00:19:23.519 --> 00:19:26.898
And only the six of us who stand accused
need take this odyssey...

213
00:19:27.056 --> 00:19:31.801
though Hawkman insists on accompanying his
spouse and Icon will act as our advocate...

214
00:19:31.960 --> 00:19:35.931
for it seems he is familiar
with intergalactic trial law.

215
00:19:36.098 --> 00:19:37.600
You're sure this is necessary?

216
00:19:37.766 --> 00:19:40.042
The Guardians of the Universe
seem to think so.

217
00:19:40.202 --> 00:19:44.150
They've sent Hal and Guy ahead to make
sure the so-called High Court of Rimbor...

218
00:19:44.306 --> 00:19:49.119
will know we come in peace.
And know we expect a fair trial.

219
00:19:49.344 --> 00:19:50.550
How long will you be gone?

220
00:19:50.712 --> 00:19:53.056
However long it takes
to clear our names. Kon-El.

221
00:19:53.215 --> 00:19:55.456
But we will be back. little brother.

222
00:19:56.218 --> 00:19:59.222
- I'll miss you.
- And I. you. M'gann.

223
00:19:59.388 --> 00:20:03.803
Oh. Perhaps you could water the plants
in my apartment while I am gone.

224
00:20:03.959 --> 00:20:05.461
Be careful. all right?

225
00:20:05.627 --> 00:20:08.506
Was about to say the same to you three.

226
00:20:08.664 --> 00:20:11.907
I fear we leave
the more dangerous task here on Earth.

227
00:20:13.368 --> 00:20:16.178
- We'll manage.
